# Scope & Definition of Done

## Out of Scope — V1

Do not implement any of the following. If a prompt requests one, respond:
> "That feature is out of scope for V1 per REQUIREMENTS.md Section 10. Should I log it as an open question for V2?"

- User accounts or authentication of any kind
- Persistent leaderboards or score storage
- Instagram OAuth integration
- Support for private Instagram accounts
- Real money, payments, or real account mutations
- Push notifications or email
- Native mobile app code

## Definition of Done

A task is complete only when all of the following are true:

- [ ] Behavior matches the relevant section of @REQUIREMENTS.md exactly
- [ ] TypeScript compiles clean: `npx tsc --noEmit` reports zero errors
- [ ] UI renders correctly at 375px (mobile) and 1280px (desktop)
- [ ] All PostHog events from Section 6 fire at the correct moment
- [ ] No secrets appear in any source file or get logged to the console
- [ ] `.env.example` reflects any new environment variables added
